#

Quick Instant Pot Borshch

40 min
$10
250 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 4

Dietary Tags:

vegetariangluten-free

Cuisine:

Eastern European

Course:

Soup

Tags:

soupinstant potquick

Description

A hearty, vibrant beet soup packed with vegetables and a touch of sour cream for a creamy finish.

Ingredients

  • beets: 2 medium, peeled and diced
  • cabbage: 2 cups, shredded
  • potatoes: 2 medium, diced
  • carrots: 2 medium, diced
  • onion: 1 medium, chopped
  • vegetable broth: 4 cups
  • tomato paste: 2 tablespoons
  • bay leaves: 2
  • sour cream: for serving
  • fresh dill: for garnish
  • salt: to taste
  • pepper: to taste
